definitions.definition: Wild ; untamed . ( of a person ) Contemptible ; unruly ; misbehaved . ( Internet slang ) Behaving in an out-of-control way due to enthrallment with a certain thought , behavior , person , etc. ( furry fandom , not comparable ) That is a feral character.

subdefinitions.definition: ( of an animal ) Wild but descended from domestic or captive ancestors ; thus, in the wild , although not necessarily of the wild type .
examples: In this region, the wild boars can be dangerous, but (perhaps counterintuitively) the feral hogs can be even worse.

main_definition: Wild ; untamed . ( of a person ) Contemptible ; unruly ; misbehaved . ( Internet slang ) Behaving in an out-of-control way due to enthrallment with a certain thought , behavior , person , etc. ( furry fandom , not comparable ) That is a feral character.

definitions.definition: Of or pertaining to the dead, funereal .

secondary_definitions: Of or pertaining to the dead, funereal .
